txt.en: 'The Mead Hall is rebuilt, but there is much to do in order to bring it to its full glory. There are many upgrades and enhancements we can make to the exterior appearance and landscaping surrounding the Hall. These small but important touches help to make a town feel unique and make it a home for its inhabitants.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
